{"tid":24613,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"每次睇返二月補選既片 就覺得好唏噓","createTime":"2016-12-05T15:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T14:46:41.000Z","uid":319,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"742e56c627593202933d1bb29d45c4cf8739ed17","tid":24613,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:44:29.000Z","msg":"個陣成個本土派氣勢都好強勁<br />\n每個本土支持者都好團結 好熱血<br />\n就算輸左都好似贏左咁開心<br />\n覺得成個本土派都好有希望<br />\n又點估到一年都無既時間<br />\n變成今日咁？唉。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58cd9f35073e98c569db6edf127c63f53ea8a2b4","tid":24613,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ltibo9dz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fltibo9dz&h=053f48ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ifybcnmg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fifybcnmg&h=82bb4820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3un9l1g4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3un9l1g4&h=8c464565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cwg4kub6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcwg4kub6&h=f42cdaf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf7a240d09f6632601f539268ed5c7fba08242ed","tid":24613,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/ltibo9dz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fltibo9dz&h=053f48ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ifybcnmg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fifybcnmg&h=82bb4820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3un9l1g4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholl